metadata.name: Paintless All Access Membership Pass 2021-2022
metadata.description:
Paintless is the fastest extension providing you with tools for your NFT buying journey. With Paintless you will feel as if you are the Flash of the NFT world. 

 Our efforts are always focused on our members and that is why we are going to keep the exclusive club very limited. Once minted no further NFTs Access passes are going to be issued - EVER. 

 Tools: 

 1. Rarity Sniper which is directly working on top of OpenSea and can determine the rarity in the same second the collection drops. We are the fastest in the market with rarity ready seconds after reveal. 

 2. Deal sniper - You let us know your price for a specific collection and we will notify you instantly when somebody posts an NFT from that collection under your desired price. By simply confirming the contract you will be able to snap it instantly.  

 3. Many more features are currently in development. 

 4. A community of like-minded NFT buyers, who can give feedback and we all together can have the best tools in the industry based on your feedback! 

 Giveaways: - For all our members we are giving away NFTs on a monthly basis! The first giveaway is going to be after we reach the first 100 members! 

 24/7 Support for all members! Discord and Twitter support for our members. We're all here to help each other. 

 Only 200 yearly members are allowed, so don't wait for too long, otherwise, the tickets are gone forever!
